data <- read.csv("Data/Cod_6_a/Cod.6a.Data.csv")

data$catch <- data$catch/1e3

No.Index <- (ncol(data) - 3)/2
No.Index
## [1] 6

Cut the catch time series to the length of index 1.

inp$timeC <- data$year[complete.cases(data$index1)]
inp$obsC <- data$catch[complete.cases(data$index1)]

plotspict.data (inp)

## SPiCT out of the box:

res <- fit.spict(inp)
